Difference Between Abstract Class & Interface
Abstract Class	Interface
Uses extends	Uses implements
Can have constructors	No constructors
Can have instance variables	Variables are public static final
Can have abstract + normal methods	Traditionally only abstract methods (modern Java also allows default and static methods)
Single inheritance	Multiple interfaces can be implemented
