Advantages
1. Hides Complexity

User doesn't need internal details.

2. Security

Internal implementation stays hidden.

3. Easy Maintenance

Change implementation without changing user code.

4. Loose Coupling

Parent doesn't depend on child implementation.

5. Reusability

Parent class reused by many child classes
